headline: Fortive Schedules Third Quarter 2025 Earnings Conference Call
summary: EVERETT, Wash., October 01, 2025--Fortive Corporation ("Fortive") (NYSE: FTV) today announced that it will webcast its earnings conference call for the third quarter 2025 on Wednesday, October 29, 2025, beginning at 12:00 p.m. ET and lasting approximately 1 hour.

headline: New Fluke GFL-1500 Quickly Locates Ground Faults to Boost Solar System Uptime
summary: Ground fault locator eliminates time-consuming fault hunts by reducing disconnections and brute-force testing individual strings, helping solar technicians work faster and safer New Fluke GFL-1500 Quickly Locates Ground Faults to Boost Solar System Uptime The Fluke GFL-1500 enables solar technicians to locate ground faults quickly, safely, using non-contact tracing.
